---
import profileImage from "../../assets/imgs/lain.jpg";
import SocialLink from "../molecules/SocialLink.astro";
---

<section id="intro" class="w-full scroll-mt-10 py-8" data-reveal>
	<div
		class="size-14 overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-[var(--color-surface)] ring-1 ring-[var(--color-border)]"
		aria-label="Avatar de Justin Andre Huertas Vargas"
	>
		<img
			class="size-full object-cover"
			src={profileImage.src}
			alt="Avatar de Justin Andre Huertas Vargas"
			loading="eager"
		/>
	</div>

	<div class="mt-5">
		<h1 class="font-sans text-base font-medium leading-6 text-white">
			Justin Andre Huertas Vargas
		</h1>
		<p
			class="mt-0.5 font-sans text-base leading-6 text-[var(--color-text-muted)]"
		>
			Frontend Engineer · Lima, Peru · GMT-5
		</p>
	</div>

	<div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-x-5 gap-y-2">
		<SocialLink href="mailto:justin.frontend08@gmail.com" label="Email" />
		<SocialLink href="#contact" label="LinkedIn" />
		<SocialLink href="#contact" label="GitHub" />
	</div>

	<div
		class="mt-8 space-y-6 font-sans text-base leading-7 text-[var(--color-text-muted)]"
	>
		<p>
			Construyo productos digitales escalables con
			<span class="text-white">React</span>, <span class="text-white"
				>Next.js</span
			>
			y <span class="text-white">TypeScript</span>, enfocados en <span class="text-white"
				>performance</span
			>, <span class="text-white">arquitectura frontend</span>, <span class="text-white"
				>seguridad</span
			> y <span class="text-white">experiencia de usuario</span>.
		</p>

		<p>
			He trabajado en <span class="text-white">plataformas bancarias</span>,
			<span class="text-white">e-commerce</span> y <span class="text-white"
				>productos enterprise</span
			> desarrollando <span class="text-white">flujos críticos</span>,
			<span class="text-white">sistemas mantenibles</span> y experiencias modernas
			alineadas a <span class="text-white">objetivos reales de negocio</span>.
		</p>

		<p>
			Mi enfoque combina <span class="text-white">ingeniería</span>, <span
				class="text-white">diseño</span
			> y <span class="text-white">producto</span> para crear aplicaciones
			<span class="text-white">rápidas</span>, <span class="text-white">robustas</span>
			y <span class="text-white">preparadas para escalar</span>.
		</p>
	</div>

	<p
		class="mt-7 inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[var(--color-text-muted)]"
	>
		<span class="size-1.5 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-accent)]"></span>
		<span>Explorando la frontera entre lógica, señal y presencia</span>
	</p>
</section>
